================================================================================
SETUP:

1.  Copy the "pircbot.jar" file from the "lib" subdirectory into the
    "lib/irc-listener" subdirectory of your Program D installation.
    
2.  Copy the "irc-listener.jar" file from the "distib" subdirectory into the
    "lib/irc-listener" subdirectory of your Program D installation.
    
3.  Open "conf/listeners.xml" from your Program D installation, and set the
    listener to enabled="true".  Set the parameters to the correct
    values, and start up!

================================================================================

